<p>
Use <a href="http://www.leonerd.org.uk/code/libtickit/">libtickit</a>.
</p>
</li>

<li>
<p>
Provide a way to be embedded in GUI/etc. backends.
</p>
</li>

<li>
<p>
Client/server model.
</p>
</li>

<li>
<p>
Database backend. See (<a href="[% base_path %]open-source/resources/databases-list/">list</a>)
</p>
</li>
</ol>
</li>

[%- END -%]

